# Prefer tsx for TypeScript runners

- Use `tsx` whenever a TypeScript runner is needed.
- Avoid `ts-node` or other TS runners in this repo.

Example:

```sh
# ✅ Do this
tsx ./scripts/my-script.ts

# ❌ Avoid this
ts-node ./scripts/my-script.ts
```
